mods.abstract: The California Magazine of Western Square and Round Dancing by the Square Dancers of Southern California. This edition includes a table of contents which lists the following: "From the Floor", "Square Dance Date Book", "On the Record and Record Report", "As I See It", "The Possible Objectives of Camps and Institutions", "Square Dance Vacations 1965", "The Dancer's Walkthru", "Ladies on the Square", "Viewpoint", "Goodbye to Pleasant Squares & Rounds", "Style Series", "14th Natl. Square Dance Convention", "Round the Outside Ring", "Sets in Order Workshop", "Gene's Western Wear Catalog", "Caller of the Month - Ron Schneider", "Paging the Roundancers - Paul and Edwina GraVette", and "Experimental Lab".
